License: GPL
Description: Fio scraper
        ===========
        
        Fio bank [http://fio.cz] transparent account data scraper.
        
        Requirements:
        --------------
         - python >= 2.7
         - python-lxml >= 2.3
        
        Usage:
        ------
        
        ::
        
                import fio
                url = ('https://www.fio.cz/scgi-bin/hermes/dz-transparent.cgi?ID_ucet=%d'
                        % account_num)
                data = fio.scrape(url)
        
        Sample output:
        --------------
        
        $ ./fio/scrape.py | tail -n 5 ::
        
                2012-05-20   -1796.00
                2012-05-22    -900.00
                2012-05-24    -400.00
                2012-05-31       1.50
                2012-06-01  -10028.00
